videos.description: Devine Ozigbo follows his blockers and runs in a 40-yard touchdown to put Nebraska on the board.
videos.headline: Nebraska's Ozigbo erupts for 40-yard TD

videos.description: Tyler Johnson climbs the ladder, grabs the pass and hold on for beautiful catch and Minnesota first down.
videos.headline: Johnson holds on for first down

videos.description: Devine Ozigbo breaks a tackle, then bursts for a 59-yard touchdown to put Nebraska up 14-0.
videos.headline: Ozigbo turns on jets for 59-yard TD

videos.description: On a QB draw, Adrian Martinez scores a 3-yard touchdown to extend Nebraska's lead to 21-0.
videos.headline: Martinez carries for TD

videos.description: On a bad handoff exchange, Nebraska's QB Adrian Martinez fumbles the ball and the ball is recovered by Minnesota's Sam Renner.
videos.headline: Nebraska fumble stalls drive

videos.description: Nebraska QB Adrian Martinez takes the snap and runs for 59 yards and later hits JD Spielman on the slant for a 9-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Martinez 's 59-yard run leads to 9-yard pass TD

videos.description: QB Zack Annexstad dishes a pass to Demetrius Douglas, who runs in a 13-yard touchdown and later Minnesota fakes the extra point attempt to get 2 points on a Matt Morse run.
videos.headline: Annexstad finds Douglas for 13-yard TD

videos.description: Minnesota's Chris Autman-Bell takes the pass from Tanner Morgan for a 69-yard gain, setting up Mohamed Ibrahim to score a 1-yard TD.
videos.headline: Minnesota's 69-yard gain sets up TD

videos.description: Off a trick play, Seth Green skies a pass for a 31-yard gain and later carries in a 4-yard touchdown to cut Nebraska's lead to 28-22.
videos.headline: Green's 31-yard catch sets up TD

videos.description: Nebraska's Adrian Martinez finds Stanley Morgan Jr. for a 35-yard touchdown, then the pair connect again for a 2-point conversion.
videos.headline: Martinez connects with Morgan for 35-yard TD

videos.description: In the red zone, Minnesota QB Tanner Morgan's pass is intercepted by Nebraska's Dedrick Young II.
videos.headline: Morgan's interception stalls potential scoring drive

videos.description: Nebraska QB Adrian Martinez launches a 67-yard pass to Stanley Morgan Jr. to extend Nebraska's lead to 46-22.
videos.headline: Martinez hits Morgan for 67-yard TD

videos.description: Minnesota QB Tanner Morgan runs in a 9-yard TD to keep the Gophers within striking distance.
videos.headline: Morgan drives in for 9-yard TD
